00:29:21,940 --> 00:29:23,580
 I really hadn't quite realized

810
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:25,580
 that what being a Foley artist entailed,

811
00:29:25,580 --> 00:29:27,040
 and I think I want it as a job.

