00:31:15,300 --> 00:31:16,140
 And there was a,

863
00:31:16,140 --> 00:31:18,460
 he said, oh, a wooden fridge.

864
00:31:18,460 --> 00:31:21,940
 It's a wonderful moment.

865
00:31:21,940 --> 00:31:23,340
 - It is amazing, but it was really,

