00:31:23,340 --> 00:31:26,100
 it was a very strong thing with the BBC for live radio,

867
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:27,780
 particularly comedy shows,

868
00:31:27,780 --> 00:31:28,900
 like The Goon Show.

