00:35:26,620 --> 00:35:28,740
 and Mario video games have the sounds

976
00:35:28,740 --> 00:35:30,420
 that would have been used in the Flintstones

977
00:35:30,420 --> 00:35:32,540
 that are sort of peppered all the way through.

978
00:35:32,540 --> 00:35:33,380
 - Really?

979
00:35:33,380 --> 00:35:34,220
 - Yeah.

980
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:35,540
 - And they made those sounds by getting a pterodactyl

981
00:35:35,540 --> 00:35:37,820
 to put their beak on a record player.

982
00:35:37,820 --> 00:35:40,060
 (laughing)

