00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:09,140
 So it would be traveling at five feet per second

995
00:36:09,140 --> 00:36:11,020
 to record it, which was really dangerous

996
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:13,580
 for anyone who had to monitor the tape

997
00:36:13,580 --> 00:36:15,420
 because if it broke off,

998
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:18,180
 it would be like shrapnel shooting out the tape.

999
00:36:18,180 --> 00:36:19,980
 And it was like a razor's edge.

1000
00:36:19,980 --> 00:36:21,700
 You would be cut to pieces if it shot.

1001
00:36:21,700 --> 00:36:23,140
 - Oh, like a ninja?

1002
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:23,980
 - Yeah, yeah.

1003
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:24,820
 So it was incredibly dangerous.

1004
00:36:24,820 --> 00:36:25,660
 - That's a great murder mystery.

