00:46:30,940 --> 00:46:33,620
 - Gorillas though, amazing animals.

1312
00:46:33,620 --> 00:46:35,460
 - They get high by spinning in circles.

1313
00:46:35,460 --> 00:46:37,420
 That's a new discovery recently.

1314
